These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, january, february, december, october, july, may
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people have 7 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, collecting, camping, filmmaking, board-games, photography
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: lily, poppy, azalea, zinnia, begonia, amaryllis, tulip
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the dutch##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growstulip and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growslily##1
13. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person who growsazalea##1
15. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the german##1
16. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
17. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Birthday      | january  | july        | october | february      | december     | september      | may     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Hobby         | collecting | filmmaking | drawing | traveling | photography  | board-games  | camping    |
| Flower     | begonia  | amaryllis         | lily     | poppy    | azalea | zinnia     | tulip     |

