 7. the person playing domino is the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the fan of rock is the police-officer##1
 9. the designer is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person playing whist##2
11. the fan of disco is the person playing poker##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person playing whist and the fan of reggae##2
14. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the writer##1
15. the analyst is on the right of the scientist##1
16. the police-officer is on the far left##1
17. the person playing snooker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
18. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
